        <h1 class="info-header"> Bio</h1>
        <h2 class="bio-pg"> I am Diogo Paixão, motion graphics and CGI generalist. </h2>
<h2> <br>
Currently I’m available for hire as a freelancer in order to develop personal and commercial projects in the realm of the visual media. This ranges from photography to 3D based animation. I'm also based in Porto, Portugal.
</h2> <h2> <br>
By employing a multidisciplinary approach and with a production based workflow in mind, the projects that I’m involved in are usually defined by a strong, filmic and narrative driven momentum. I am a bit more comfortable with production and post-production jobs, when weighting these phases against pre-production or direction tasks. Said jobs might include, Design, Rendering, Modeling, Simulation, Compositing, Color Correction, Video Editing, Animation, Look Development, Concept Development and Pipeline Optimization.  </h2>
<h2> <br>
Most levels of my theoretical and technical expertise come from a self-taught environment and a strong will to keep expanding my set of skills.</h2>


